multicore cache coherency ... three things 

TCR_VALUE --- SH0 & SH1, inner shareable   mmu.h
pgtables -- MM_SH_INNER, inner shareable mmu.h
S3_1_c15_c2_1 -- (cortex a53 specific. armstub sets this. if we boot w/o armstub, we must set it up)
https://developer.arm.com/documentation/ddi0500/j/BABGHHEJ
https://u-boot.denx.narkive.com/l1g1jI7V/patch-armv8-enable-cpuectlr-smpen-for-data-coherency

