overall malloc code... 

fixed a silly bug in reserve_pages()... count the page indx wrong....
     framebuffer region and malloc region are both reserved, and overlapped. 
     which caused memory corruption in surface flinger. 
and this double reservation was missed due to reserve_page() bug

now fixed reserve_pages()... also update kernel layout, so that fb region and 
malloc regions are disjoint....


